            David Dimbleby's famous moments from 25 years of Question Time
            Question Time presenter David Dimbleby was given a standing ovation as he hosted his final show after almost 25 years in the hot seat.The programme will continue in the new year with Fiona Bruce moderating the debate.Here are some of the most memorable - and unusual - moments from Dimbleby's tenure.
                
                        14 Dec 2018
                    
                
        
